uk.ac.ebi.pride.utilities.data.core

Class ContactRole

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ebi.pride.utilities.data.core.ContactRole

  • public class ContactRole
extends Object
    Contact Role is a class to define the role of an Specific Contact (Organization or Person)in the context of the Experiment a role is defined as CvParams () The role that a Contact plays in an organization or with respect to the associating class. A Contact may have several Roles within scope, and as such, associations to ContactRole allow the use of a Contact in a certain manner. Examples might include a provider, or a data analyst.
